{
  "texts": [
    "Some methods have also probed into contactless physiological signals with deep learning for CMER; a study employed a method that combined heart rate and spatiotemporal features to recognize micro-expressions [98].",
    "Employing pre-trained models for CMERThe progressive strides in deep learning have paved the way for sophisticated, large-scale, pre-trained models that are now finding application across diverse fields.",
    "Pre-trained models are the deep learning models trained on large datasets.",
    "These models can be fine-tuned or re-trained for a similar task without training from scratch.",
    "These models have emerged as a particularly effective tool for CMER, achieving superior results when fine-tuned for CMER."
  ]
}